## Response Timeline

| Milestone | Target |
|-----------|--------|
| Acknowledgement of report | ≤5 business days |
| Detailed response (next steps / severity assessment) | ≤10 business days |
| Fix or mitigation available | Depends on severity (see below) |
| Coordinated public disclosure | See Disclosure Policy below |

**Severity-based remediation targets:**

| CVSS Score | Severity | Fix target |
|------------|----------|-----------|
| 9.0–10.0 | Critical | ≤7 days |
| 7.0–8.9 | High | ≤30 days |
| 4.0–6.9 | Medium | ≤90 days |
| 0.1–3.9 | Low | Next scheduled release |

